From @euhmeuh initial version.
Print text using flowers for slack.

Works with the alphabet, space and exclamation point.

Usage: sayitwith.py [-h] [--spaced] type text

Print some things.

positional arguments:
  type        Say it with what ? flowers, catz
  text        The text to print, letters must be within : !, *, 3, <, a, c, b,
              e, d, g, f, i, h, k, j, m, l, o, n, q, p, s, r, u, t, w, v, y,
              x, z, <space>

optional arguments:
  -h, --help  show this help message and exit
  --spaced    Spaces between letters (default: False)

